{"tid":529443,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人讀過催眠課程?","createTime":"2018-01-14T18:54:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-16T16:51:42.000Z","uid":68484,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4da6cfcc8b55713db4ce977b37d1b592802cb2de","tid":529443,"uid":68484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T18:54:19.000Z","msg":"自己而家讀緊同精神健康有關嘅course<br />\n所以對相關嘅野好有興趣<br />\n之後喺朋友口中聽到催眠 有d想學<br />\n我自己之後就上網search<br />\n發覺好似冇乜邊間有認受性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有d仲話部份centre會sell埋人讀咩改善人生嘅洗腦課程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n比人洗腦 性格大變之餘 仲要比人呃錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以就想問下有冇巴絲上過催眠課程 講下類似課程嘅內容<br />\n或者係邊間centre比較信得過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又或者討論下催眠嘅野又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06e484f3c3b6b33c8a7e1451e92d37e4b4bc2575","tid":529443,"uid":6869,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T18:56:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2f3aa458a9091da17365d8c015c2751e4c709ed5","tid":529443,"uid":4824,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T18:59:22.000Z","msg":"希望有日香港所有洗腦課程都係犯法<br />\n佢地班害人既仆街全部終身監禁<br />\n享受一下肉體被控制既滋味"},{"pid":"ab23ecccfbf77feab5bbaa925f628ffc4e992c34","tid":529443,"uid":123456,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T19:01:40.000Z","msg":"買書睇ok嫁啦"},{"pid":"a4b5db739e95fc139aa6934ad794e717f2e56b0f","tid":529443,"uid":23416,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T19:12:45.000Z","msg":"一滴兩滴"},{"pid":"2d33cdb84c360c3c9e2853467e7025d03acf4952","tid":529443,"uid":36702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T19:19:31.000Z","msg":"有  一試堂就比人催眠左 報左一年 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81d9156f3e1f383e809b4e2580dc212b344b4ded","tid":529443,"uid":48796,"lik